 ¬                       Razor 1911 News & Announcements                      ¬
 ¬                      ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~                     ¬
 ¬    Sad sad sad, it's a shame that PDM made some boo-boo's with their       ¬
 ¬    release of Resident Evil.  The main boo-boo being that voices are       ¬
 ¬    required to know what the hell is going on in the game.  There is no    ¬
 ¬    text dialogue anywhere in the game.  Well, if you do the math the       ¬
 ¬    original release of Resident Evil from Paradigm is 73 disks, then you   ¬
 ¬    get 45 more disks of NEEDED speech.  Without it, the game is unplayable ¬
 ¬    that makes a nice fat 118 disks?!!  Not to mention that the sound was   ¬
 ¬    removed too?  Jesus guys, we love you and all..but get a clue.          ¬
 ¬                                                                            ¬
 ¬    What we here at the Razor family bring you, is a SOLID and within the   ¬
 ¬    LIMIT release of Resident Evil.  Speech, sound fx, and WORKING 3DFX..   ¬
 ¬    it's all there boys.  Read BEOWULF aka GOD's explanation on how and     ¬
 ¬    why we did it.  This game is BONE-A-FIDE BADASS!  Also, make sure to    ¬ 
 ¬    check out Keys.txt for an explanation on some of the keyboard commands  ¬ 
 ¬    and stuff we discovered PLAY-TESTING Resident Evil.  Imagine that,      ¬
 ¬    testing...anyway, enjoy yet another fantastic release from our family   ¬
 ¬    to yours...ENJOY!                                                       ¬
 ¬                                                                            ¬
